## Testing Components

Components should have tests in `__tests__` directories adjacent to the component:

```
src/components/form/button/
  ├── AuButton.tsx
  ├── AuButtonKindE.ts
  ├── AuButtonSizeE.ts
  ├── auButton.scss
  └── __tests__/
      └── AuButton.test.tsx
```

**Test Guidelines:**

- Test user interactions
- Test conditional rendering
- Test accessibility
- Don't test simple prop passing
- Use `@testing-library/react` for component tests

